


=Payment Methods=

This application lets you keep track of all forms of payment that use the entity.

[formaspago-listado.png]

==List of payment==

In the list of payment you will find the most important pillars of registration:

- **Ref.:** Numeric code that identifies the payment.
- **Name:** Name payment.
- **Description:** Description of the method of payment.


===Listing Options===

On each record. You can perform a series of actions that are represented by the following icons:

- [fa-search] [fa-pencil] [fa-trash] Check / Edit / Delete Record.


===Filter Options===

For more information about the filter options listed in the **[ayuda general http://viewpdf/page=home]**.

==Form of payment==

This is the application for payment, with it you can add, modify and view all data of payment classified into different tabs: main data, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Data tab of payment===

In this tab you can view and modify the main details of the payment. Here we relate all information fields.

[formaspago-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** Name payment.
- **Description:** Description of the method of payment.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a form of payment Campos.**

